<text id="05-examples" title="AI Diff Size Discipline Worked Example" version="1.1.0" est_tokens="600" depth="essential">
  <summary>Worked example: PR-1432 AI diff of 142 LOC for a feature lands as verdict=pass.</summary>

  <section title="Scenario">
    <p>Solo dev used Claude Code to add a `/health` endpoint with 5 files touched. Caps respected; tests included.</p>
  </section>

  <section title="Inputs">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "pr_id": "PR-1432",
  "raw_diff_loc": 230,
  "tests_loc": 88
}
]]></code>
  </section>

  <section title="Output">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "pr_id": "PR-1432",
  "loc_touched": 142,
  "loc_test_touched": 88,
  "files_touched": 5,
  "semantic_units": [
    "feature"
  ],
  "verdict": "pass"
}
]]></code>
  </section>

  <section title="Validator run">
    <code lang="text"><![CDATA[
$ python scripts/validate-ai-diff-size-discipline.py --file artefact.json
OK
]]></code>
  </section>
</text>
